{
  "stem": "10745.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In 1939, there was a lot-- a lot-- I would say a lot, maybe-- Jewish people from all over were running away.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they came through our town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I met people from Germany that said the Germans were killing and they were taking everything away and Jews were dying from hunger and all kinds-- and on their way to Russia.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So in 1939, we already felt.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we, in 1939, were better off than before, because the Russians gave us better freedom from anti-Semites than before.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The only thing was my father was like a capitalist there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So he went to them, and he said, you can have the bakery.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They really appreciated that he gave away the bakery.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So  they said, because you gave the bakery, you'll be the manager.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He says, OK, I'll run it, you supply the flour and whatever you need, and we'll make.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But he was not a good manager for them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "From-- from each bag of flour, you had to give out so much-- so much bread.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he couldn't do that, because he was baking out a good loaf of bread, and everything else.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they had to have a bread that has lots of water in it, and it weighs a lot.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he says, if that case, I'm too sick to run it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You run it on your own.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they took over, and they ran it on their own.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took it over in the house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When did the Russians come in?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1939.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's what I'm saying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In 1939, the Russians came in, they were there for two years.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At that time, even when the Russians came in, I say, was better for me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In school, the teacher was still there that used to call me Jew.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
